definition: to happen/to occur/to take place/to break out
to send out/to show (one's feeling)/to issue/to develop/to make a bundle of money/classifier for gunshots (rounds)
to be born/to give birth/life/to grow/raw/uncooked/student
to have sexual relations with sb/to have dealings with

sentences.english: Other violence occurred at Friendship Road and at Liberation Road, they said.
sentences.chinese: 他们说还有其它的暴力事件发生在友谊路和解放大道。

sentences.english: Many disaster will happen every day in the world.
sentences.chinese: 在这个世界上，天天都邑发生很多灾难性的工作。

sentences.english: Two cases of cholera, one of which has ended fatally, have occurred here.
sentences.chinese: 这里发生过两起霍乱病例，其中一人已经死亡。

sentences.english: Corneal ulcers occur most often in patients who use extended-wear soft contact lenses.
sentences.chinese: 角膜溃疡最常发生于长期使用软性角膜接触镜的病人。

sentences.english: At (long) last we found out what had really happened.
sentences.chinese: 最后，我们终于弄清了实际发生的情况。

sentences.english: It's not going to happen overnight.
The direction of light reflected from an object depends on its alignment.
sentences.chinese: 光线的方向会根据对象的位置发生反射。

sentences.english: Thinking structure in childhood in the development of the critical period.
sentences.chinese: 思维结构在儿童期处于发生发展的关键期。

sentences.english: No cases have been reported outside Uige for the past five weeks.
sentences.chinese: 在过去5周内在威热省之外未报告发生病例。

sentences.english: Which, briefly, is like an explosion in a spear factory.
sentences.chinese: 简单地说，就像兵工厂发生了爆炸。

sentences.english: This event long antedates the arrival of Columbus in America.
sentences.chinese: 这件事的发生远在哥伦布到达美洲之前。

sentences.english: What happens in disputes between direct buyer and seller?
sentences.chinese: 直接购买者与出售者之间发生哪些争端？

sentences.english: What happens when you mix flour with water?
sentences.chinese: 你混合水和面粉的时候会发生什么事呢？

sentences.english: The heart is one of first organs to form during organogenesis in the vertebrate.
sentences.chinese: 心脏是脊椎动物器官发生过程中最早形成的器官之一。

sentences.english: Patients in both groups re-occur without intraoperative awareness.
sentences.chinese: 两组患者术后回访无术中知晓发生。

sentences.english: The last lane is Method, indicating where the lock contends.
sentences.chinese: 最后一列是方法，表明锁竞争是在什么位置发生的。
